snippet.textDisplay:
MashAllah this is very beautifully presented by Atif Aslam. But I have one MAJOR OBJECTION on it and all the people reading this comment will definitely agree with my point. 
The transition between the changing of names of Allah is "vanishing effect" and it looks as if something is getting dissolved in air and hence disappeared.
I don't think this is the correct transition of words especially for the Names of Almighty Allah Who can never be vanished or dissolved (NAOZOBILLAH).
If possible please make a noble attempt to modify this transition. JazakAllah Khair
